annotationA: Glutamate decarboxylase; Catalyzes the production of GABA; Belongs to the group II decarboxylase family
annotationB: Vesicular glutamate transporter, isoform A; L-glutamate transmembrane transporter activity; high-affinity inorganic phosphate:sodium symporter activity; neurotransmitter transporter activity.
